		<forum>http://forum.kodi.tv/showthread.php?tid=160558</forum>
		<source>https://github.com/matke-84/script.extendedinfo</source>
		<news>
Version 5.6.1
* Added support for Kodi Matrix
Version 5.6.2
* Bug fixes
		</news>
